BEGIN INSERT INTO <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_ACTUALIZA_ICCID_TMP_TB") ?> SELECT T2.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI ,T2.MIN ,TO_DATE(SUBSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,INSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|',1,LENGTH(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG) - LENGTH(REPLACE(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|')))+1,6),'YYMMDD') AS FEC_ESTADO_BSCS ,SUBSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,INSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|',1,LENGTH(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG) - LENGTH(REPLACE(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|')))+1,6) AS F_ESTADO_ACTUAL ,CASE WHEN LENGTH(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG) - LENGTH(REPLACE(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|')) - 1 = 0 THEN SUBSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,INSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|',1)+1,6) ELSE SUBSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,INSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|',1,LENGTH(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG) - LENGTH(REPLACE(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|')) - 1)+1,6) END AS F_ESTADO_ANTERIOR ,T1.CS_STAT_CHNG ,T1.ID_CAUSAL ,CASE SUBSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,LENGTH(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG)-1,1) WHEN 'a' THEN 1 WHEN 's' THEN 3 WHEN 'd' THEN 9 END AS ESTADO_BSCS FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_DATA_BSCS_TMP_TB") ?> T1 JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB") ?> T2 ON (T1.DN_NUM = T2.MIN) WHERE INSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,'|') > 0 AND T2.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI IN (1,3,9) AND CASE T2.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI WHEN CASE SUBSTR(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG,LENGTH(T1.CS_STAT_CHNG)-1,1) WHEN 'a' THEN 1 WHEN 's' THEN 3 WHEN 'd' THEN 9 END THEN 'Bien' ELSE 'Mal' END = 'Mal'; COMMIT; END;

OdiSqlUnload "-FILE=#PRY_FABR_DIG.V_008_DIR_REMOTOBase_total_ODI.csv" "-DRIVER=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_JAVA_DRIVER") ?>" "-URL=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_JAVA_URL") ?>" "-USER=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_USER_NAME") ?>" "-PASS=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_ENCODED_PASS") ?>" "-FILE_FORMAT=VARIABLE" "-FIELD_SEP=#PRY_FABR_DIG.V_008_DELIMI_PLANO" "-ROW_SEP=\r\n" "-DATE_FORMAT=yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss" "-CHARSET_ENCODING=UTF-8" "-XML_CHARSET_ENCODING=UTF-8" "-FETCH_SIZE=100000" SELECT 'SK_ESTADO_BENEFI' ,'COD_ESTADO' ,'NUM_DOC' ,'CO_ID' ,'ID_BENEFICIARIO' ,'CUSTCODE' ,'ICCID' ,'CUSTOMER_ID' ,'MIN' ,'TMCODE' ,'META' ,'FEC_OPER_INI' ,'FEC_OPER_FIN' FROM DUAL UNION ALL SELECT TO_CHAR(T2.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI) ,TO_CHAR(T3.COD_ESTADO) ,TO_CHAR(T2.NUM_DOC) ,TO_CHAR(CO_ID) ,TO_CHAR(T1.ID_BENEFICIARIO) ,TO_CHAR(CUSTCODE) ,TO_CHAR(''''||ICCID||'') AS ICCID ,TO_CHAR(CUSTOMER_ID) ,TO_CHAR(T2.MIN) ,TO_CHAR(TMCODE) ,TO_CHAR(NVL(META,0)) AS META ,TO_CHAR(FEC_OPER_INI) AS FEC_OPER_INI ,TO_CHAR(FEC_OPER_FIN) AS FEC_OPER_FIN FROM MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB T1 LEFT JOIN MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T2 ON (T2.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END)) JOIN MINTIC_ESTADO_BENEF_DIM_TB_T1 T3 ON (T2.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = T3.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI)

OdiSqlUnload "-FILE=#PRY_FABR_DIG.V_008_DIR_REMOTOBeneficiarios_Desactivos_ODI.csv" "-DRIVER=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_JAVA_DRIVER") ?>" "-URL=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_JAVA_URL") ?>" "-USER=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_USER_NAME") ?>" "-PASS=<?=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_ENCODED_PASS") ?>" "-FILE_FORMAT=VARIABLE" "-FIELD_SEP=#PRY_FABR_DIG.V_008_DELIMI_PLANO" "-ROW_SEP=\r\n" "-DATE_FORMAT=yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss" "-CHARSET_ENCODING=UTF-8" "-XML_CHARSET_ENCODING=UTF-8" "-FETCH_SIZE=100000" SELECT 'OBSERVACION' ,'NUM_DOC BENEFICIARIO' ,'MIN' ,'CODIGO DE ESTADO' ,'DESCRIPCION COD ESATDO' ,'MUNICIPIO - DEPARTAMENTO' ,'ETAPA' ,'ID_BENEFICIARIO' FROM DUAL UNION ALL SELECT * FROM( SELECT NULL ,TO_CHAR(CASE WHEN T2.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T2.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T2.NUM_DOC END) AS NUM_DOC_BENEFI ,TO_CHAR(T1.MIN) AS MIN ,TO_CHAR(T1.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI) AS SK_ESTADO_BENEFI ,TO_CHAR(T5.COD_ESTADO) AS COD_ESTADO ,TO_CHAR(T4.NOM_DEPARTAMENTO||'-'||T4.NOM_CENTRO_POBLADO) AS MUNICIO_DEPTO ,TO_CHAR(T2.META) AS META ,TO_CHAR(T2.ID_BENEFICIARIO) AS ID_BENEFICIARIO FROM MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T1 JOIN MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB T2 ON (T1.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T2.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T2.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T2.NUM_DOC END)) JOIN MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TB_T1 T3 ON (T2.SK_ETAPA = T3.SK_ETAPA) JOIN TBL_DIM_MUNICIPIOS_DANE_T1 T4 ON (T2.SK_MUNICIPIO = T4.SK_MUNICIPIO) JOIN MINTIC_ESTADO_BENEF_DIM_TB_T1 T5 ON (T1.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = T5.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI) WHERE T1.SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = 9 UNION SELECT 'El numero de documento '||NUM_DOC_Q1||' fue reemplazado con el beneficiario '||NUM_DOC_Q2||' para el ID_Beneficiario '||ID_BENEFICIARIO_Q1||' el dia '||FECHA_ESTADO_Q1||'' OBSERVACION ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_Q2) ,TO_CHAR(T2.MIN_Q2) ,'1' AS SK_ESTADO_BENEFI ,'Activo' AS ESTADO ,NULL AS MUNICIO_DEPTO ,TO_CHAR(META_Q1) ,TO_CHAR(ID_BENEFICIARIO_Q1) FROM ( SELECT T1.ID_BENEFICIARIO AS ID_BENEFICIARIO_Q1 ,T2.NUM_DOC AS NUM_DOC_Q1 ,T1.META AS META_Q1 ,T2.FECHA_ESTADO AS FECHA_ESTADO_Q1 FROM MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB T1 JOIN MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T2 ON ((CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END) = T2.NUM_DOC) WHERE SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = 2) T1 JOIN ( SELECT T1.ID_BENEFICIARIO AS ID_BENEFICIARIO_Q2 ,T2.NUM_DOC AS NUM_DOC_Q2 ,T1.META AS META_Q2 ,T1.MIN AS MIN_Q2 FROM MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB T1 JOIN MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T2 ON ((CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END) = T2.NUM_DOC) WHERE SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = 1) T2 ON (T1.ID_BENEFICIARIO_Q1 = T2.ID_BENEFICIARIO_Q2 AND T1.META_Q1 = T2.META_Q2))

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(1) > 0 THEN COUNT(1) ELSE 0 END CONTEO FROM( SELECT B.CAUSAL_DESACTIVACION||' - con fecha de envio a activar de '||C.FECREGIS ,TO_CHAR(A.NUMERODOCUMENTO) AS NUM_DOC ,TO_CHAR(B.MIN) AS MIN ,TO_CHAR(B.NUM_DOC) AS NUM_DOC_BENE ,NULL AS NUM_DOC_PLAN ,NULL AS MIN_PLAN ,NULL AS BENEFICIARIO ,'Error Activaciones' FROM MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB B LEFT JOIN MINTIC_MASSIVE_ACTIVA_TMP_TB A ON (''''||A.CODMIN||'''' = ''''||B.MIN||'''') LEFT JOIN MINTIC_ACTIVACIONES_TB C ON (A.CODMIN = C.CODMIN AND B.MIN = C.CODMIN ) --WHERE PROCESS_RESULT = '0' WHERE SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = 4 AND CAUSAL_DESACTIVACION != 'La maestra es invlida La maestra esta errada ,' UNION ALL SELECT CASE WHEN ERRORES = 'E-Solo tenemos data cargada en Base_Mintic-E-Solo se encuentra informacion en Base_Mintic y Duplas_Mintic-E-Solo se encuentra informacion en Base_Mintic y Plan_entrega_Mintic--' THEN 'E-Solo tenemos data cargada en Base_Mintic' ELSE ERRORES END AS ERRORES ,NUM_DOC_MILLA ,MIN_BENE ,NUM_DOC_BENE ,NUM_DOC_PLAN ,MIN_PLAN ,BENEFICIARIO ,ERRR FROM( SELECT TRIM(MAX(CASE WHEN NUM_DOC_BENE IS NULL AND NUM_DOC_PLAN IS NULL THEN 'E-Solo tenemos data cargada en Base_Mintic' END)||'-'|| MAX(CASE WHEN NUM_DOC_PLAN IS NULL THEN 'E-Solo se encuentra informacion en Base_Mintic y Duplas_Mintic' END)||'-'|| MAX(CASE WHEN NUM_DOC_BENE IS NULL THEN 'E-Solo se encuentra informacion en Base_Mintic y Plan_entrega_Mintic' END)||'-'|| MAX(CASE WHEN VAL_MIN = 'Mines Mal' AND MIN_BENE IS NULL THEN 'E-Falta cargar informacion de Duplas' END))/*||'-'|| MAX(CASE WHEN VAL_MIN = 'Mines Mal' AND MIN_PLAN IS NULL THEN 'E-Falta cargar informacion de plan de entrega' END))||'-'|| MAX(CASE WHEN VAL_MIN = 'Mines Mal' THEN 'E-Los mines cargados para Duplas y plan entrega no son iguales' END)) */ AS ERRORES ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_MILLA) AS NUM_DOC_MILLA ,TO_CHAR(MIN_BENE) AS MIN_BENE ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_BENE) AS NUM_DOC_BENE ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_PLAN) AS NUM_DOC_PLAN ,TO_CHAR(MIN_PLAN) AS MIN_PLAN ,TO_CHAR(BENEFICIARIO) AS BENEFICIARIO ,'Otro tipo de error' AS ERRR FROM ( SELECT T4.BENEFICIARIO ,CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END AS NUM_DOC_MILLA ,T2.NUM_DOC AS NUM_DOC_BENE ,T3.NUM_DOC AS NUM_DOC_PLAN ,T2.MIN AS MIN_BENE ,T3.MIN AS MIN_PLAN ,CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END) = T2.NUM_DOC AND (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END) = T3.NUM_DOC AND T2.NUM_DOC = T3.NUM_DOC AND T2.MIN = T3.MIN THEN 'Bien' ELSE 'Validar' END VALIDA ,CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END) = T2.NUM_DOC AND (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END) = T3.NUM_DOC AND T2.NUM_DOC = T3.NUM_DOC THEN 'Cedulas bien' ELSE 'Cedulas Mal' END VAL_CC ,CASE WHEN NVL(T2.MIN,'0') = NVL(T3.MIN,'0') THEN 'Mines bien' ELSE 'Mines Mal' END VAL_MIN FROM MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB T1 LEFT JOIN MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T2 ON (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END = T2.NUM_DOC) LEFT JOIN MINTIC_INFO_PLAN_ENTREGA_TB T3 ON (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END = T3.NUM_DOC ) JOIN MINTIC_CATEG_BENEFI_DIM_TB_T1 T4 ON (T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = T4.SK_CATEG_BENEF)) WHERE VALIDA NOT IN ('Bien') GROUP BY TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_MILLA) ,TO_CHAR(MIN_BENE) ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_BENE) ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC_PLAN) ,TO_CHAR(MIN_PLAN) ,TO_CHAR(BENEFICIARIO) ,'Otro tipo de error') A UNION ALL SELECT 'Esta linea se encuentra activa con otra causal' ,NULL NUM_DOC_MILLA ,TO_CHAR(MIN) MIN_BENE ,TO_CHAR(NUM_DOC) NUM_DOC_BENE ,NULL NUM_DOC_PLAN ,NULL MIN_PLAN ,NULL BENEFICIARIO ,'Posible linea activa con otra causal' FROM MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB WHERE SK_ESTADO_BENEFI = -1 UNION SELECT 'E-Falta cargar informacion de plan de entrega' AS ERRORES ,TO_CHAR(T1.NUM_DOC) AS NUM_DOC_MILLA ,TO_CHAR(T1.MIN) AS MIN_BENE ,TO_CHAR(T1.NUM_DOC) AS NUM_DOC_BENE ,TO_CHAR(T2.NUM_DOC) AS NUM_DOC_PLAN ,TO_CHAR(T2.MIN) AS MIN_PLAN ,NULL BENEFICIARIO ,'Otro tipo de error' AS ERRR FROM MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T1 LEFT JOIN MINTIC_INFO_PLAN_ENTREGA_TB T2 ON (T1.MIN = T2.MIN) WHERE T2.MIN IS NULL UNION SELECT 'E-Informacion faltante en ODI solo esta en BSCS' AS ERRORES ,NULL AS NUM_DOC_MILLA ,TO_CHAR(T1.DN_NUM) AS MIN_BENE ,NULL AS NUM_DOC_BENE ,NULL AS NUM_DOC_PLAN ,NULL AS MIN_PLAN ,NULL BENEFICIARIO ,'Otro tipo de error' AS ERRR FROM MINTIC_DATA_BSCS_TMP_TB T1 LEFT JOIN MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB T2 ON (T1.DN_NUM = T2.MIN) WHERE T2.MIN IS NULL) A
